\n佢啲車下下咁重"},{"pid":"ec396dc5d45febad0a1b44268915fd3831744162","tid":1576834,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"以前都有單野<br />\n中國貨當歐洲貨用<br />\n結果電鑬個純絕緣體著火"},{"pid":"fbd991bbda0c4a66df8d1e37398507990e42643e","tid":1576834,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:36:42.000Z","msg":"港鐵：英國佬錯，強國車好安全"}]}